 (Eds: Resending to fix coding, eliminate garble)  &HT;     HOUSTON COMPANY WILL FLY YOU TO THE MOON 
 &HT;     By STEVE RUBENSTEIN 
 &HT;     c.2000 San Francisco Chronicle  
<TEXT>
<P>
   A Houston company is selling tickets to the moon for $12,500,
but you have to be dead first.
</P>
