the film ``Battlefield Earth,'' to be released this summer, because
it is based on the 1982 science-fiction novel by L. Ron Hubbard,
who was also the founder of Scientology, and because the film was
the pet project of John Travolta, who has made no secret of his
dedication to Scientology. Could this be a sneaky attempt to lure
