   FINANCIAL
</P>
<P>
   (Will move in ``f'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   MICROSOFT-ANTITRUST (Washington) _ The Microsoft Corp. delivered
its formal response in federal court to the remedy proposal from
the Justice Department and 17 states asking that the company be
broken into two parts. By Joel Brinkley.
</P>
