   INTERNET-TAXES (Washington) _ The House Commerce Committee
extends a moratorium on any Internet taxation for five years. By
Lizette Alvarez.
</P>
<P>
   NEW YORK
</P>
<P>
   (Will move in ``a'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   NY-GIULIANI-WIFE (New York) _ Mayor Rudolph Giuliani announced
Wednesday that he was separating from his wife, Donna Hanover. He
said that as he battles prostate cancer he will need Judith Nathan,
the woman he describes as a ``very good'' friend, ``more now than
maybe I did before.'' By Elizabeth Bumiller.
</P>
