Reserve, continues its slump. It's beginning to sink into investors
that the Fed is not going to ease up any time soon. And a few
voices of concern are being raised about whether the Fed will boost
rates too much. Others still think a little pain now is better than
dealing with high inflation later on. (McNaughton, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 15.
