<P>
   ELIAN-MAIN _ ATLANTA _ News of the day: Portions of the Gonzalez
family arrive in Atlanta from Miami. Anti-return group expected to
demonstrate this afternoon in front of federal courthouse _ one of
many skedded at U.S. courthouses in major cities as a show of
support for keeping Elian in the US. (Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25. WITH PHOTOS.
