   WITH
</P>
<P>
   ELIAN-RALLY _ Protesters plan to be at federal buildings in 13
major cities today in an attempt to keep Elian Gonzalez in the
United States. Members of Miami's Cuban Democracy Movement are
organizing today's protests. They promise that the demonstrations
in cities like Chicago, Washington, New York, Los Angeles and Miami
will all be peaceful. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
