vote today to remove the Confederate flag from the top of the
Statehouse. A memorial on the capitol's grounds that is the focus
of the debate was vandalized early today. The words ``take it down,
don't put it here'' were spray painted in red on the monument to
Confederate war dead in front of the Statehouse. (Manuel, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
