</P>
<P>
   KLEENEX COTTONELLE TOILET PAPER
</P>
<P>
   12 double rolls
</P>
<P>
   Webvan: $7.94 for two packages of six double rolls. (The 12-roll
pack is not offered.)
</P>
<P>
   Kroger: $7.99
</P>
<P>
   Ingles: $7.29
</P>
