would have a happy ending, like ``Forrest Gump.''
</P>
<P>
   ``PRIORITIES''
</P>
<P>
   Provides your daily dose of affirmation. To buy a magazine that
is subtitled ``The Journal of Professional and Personal Success,''
you just have to be something special. They offer a lightweight
feature on former Phoenix Suns Coach Danny Ainge, who gave up one
