Brown troupe members rehearsing ``Rapture to Leon James.'' Brown's
new jazz-inspired dance piece - which received its New York
premiere on Tuesday night at the Joyce Theater - is a beauty, a
perfect blend of the vernacular and the abstract. (Ruby
Washington/The New York Times)
</P>
<P>
